    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 5'>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='104732' id='3' type-v2='text' w='95885' x='1746' y='996'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Restaurant Customer Behavior &amp; Tipping Analysis</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Goal: Understand customer spending and tipping patterns to improve service strategy.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Page 1 — Overall Customer Overview</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>The restaurant recorded 4,828 total bill value with an average bill of around 20.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Male customers spend slightly more (Avg bill = 21) compared to female customers (Avg bill = 18).</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>72% population is male on weekends.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Dinner dominates restaurant activity, accounting for 72% of visits, while lunch contributes 28%.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Around 38% of customers are smokers, which may influence seating and service patterns.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Saturday and Sunday generate the highest number of bills, indicating strong weekend demand.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Business Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Weekend evenings represent the primary revenue opportunity, so staffing and service capacity should be optimized during these periods.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Page 2 — Customer Spending &amp; Group Behavior</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Most customers visit in groups of 2, which represents the largest portion of dining parties.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>The maximum tip percentage occurs on Sunday, suggesting customers are more generous during weekend dining.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>There is a clear positive relationship between total bill and tip amount — higher bills generally lead to higher tips.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Larger groups tend to generate higher total tips, although tip distribution varies.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Business Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Encouraging group dining experiences and upselling menu items can increase total bills and consequently tip earnings.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Page 3 — Customer Segmentation Analysis</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>The average tip from smokers and non-smokers is relatively similar, indicating smoking status has minimal impact on tipping behavior.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Male customers provide slightly higher average tips compared to female customers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>The heatmap shows male customers dominate dining visits across most days, particularly on weekends.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Tip distribution remains fairly consistent across customer groups, suggesting tipping culture is relatively stable.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Business Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Service strategies should focus on bill value and dining experience rather than customer demographics, as these factors influence tips more strongly.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Page 4 — Spending Distribution</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Most customer bills fall between 10 and 20, representing the restaurant&apos;s core spending range.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Dinner transactions dominate the higher bill ranges, confirming dinner service generates larger revenue per customer.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Very high bills (above 40) are relatively rare but contribute significantly to overall revenue.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Business Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Menu pricing and promotions should target the 10–20 spending segment, while premium menu items can capture higher-value customers during dinner.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Final Recommendation Page</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Key Business Recommendations</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Focus on weekend dinner service, as it drives the majority of revenue.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Encourage group dining promotions, since most tables consist of 2–4 customers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Introduce upselling strategies to increase average bill value and tips.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Optimize staff allocation during peak weekend hours.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial Rounded MT Bold'>Offer premium dinner menu options to capture high-spending customers.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
